Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This great war began from a single confrontation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.92,0:00:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Many different people with different ideals have clashed, bringing forth great tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is truly regrettable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I too have suffered from this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel both shame and regret for our use of a power not meant for human hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.21,0:00:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, here and now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I claim my birthright to Rayregalia Vers Rayvers's title
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.92,0:00:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and hereby name myself Empress of Vers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.62,0:00:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I also announce my engagement to Count Cruhteo of the Orbital Knights' Thirty-Seven Clans.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,As the imperial family of the Vers Empire, \Nwe hereby extend the olive branch of peace to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of the Empress of Vers,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.18,0:01:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I order all Orbital Knights \Nwhom this broadcast may reach
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.45,0:01:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to cease hostilities at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.72,0:01:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the princess not poised to found a new dynasty with Count Troyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What will we do about the all-out offensive against Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Halt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Put the forces on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.78,0:01:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us await further developments.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It is no wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.67,0:01:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Count Troyard is still little more than Terran rabble.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.24,0:01:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ascension to royalty was always beyond his reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.02,0:01:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Harklight, we withdraw to the moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Slaine...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are they still fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.78,0:01:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The princess ordered them to stand down!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The forces from the moon base still want to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:01:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay focused!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:01:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.78,0:02:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That Princess Asseylum just now—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Empress Asseylum—\Nsounded just like the one I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's just as Second Lieutenant Kaizuka predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that order for a ceasefire must be real as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemies we're engaging \Naren't standing down, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Any word from HQ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No new orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're to continue the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.78,0:02:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither the moon base nor the Landing Castles show any intent to cease hostilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Empress Asseylum?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.98,0:02:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The earlier transmission was broadcast from Count Mazuurek's Landing Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she abandon the moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Or has a schism developed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Count Troyard, how are we to proceed with Her Highness' orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologies, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an unexpected turn of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.65,0:03:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Lemrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What truly matters is royal blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you have Aldnoah activation rights,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,your dream is still within reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I will stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only place I can call home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you for your kindness, Princess Lemrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that a heartless thing to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen many things while flying through those lights.{c-beams glittering in the dark, etc}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Many things?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The future?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The good and the bad alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All I could see was the immediate future,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but I thought I understood everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Many things unfolded just as I foresaw,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.53,0:04:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost sight of what was truly important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Resupply.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Count Troyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would Princess Asseylum say such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Slaine...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Patch me through to the command center.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I will address all units,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.39,0:05:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,including the Stygis Platoon out in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You have ten minutes to evacuate the moon base!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender to the Earth forces \Ntogether with the Landing Castles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We are abandoning the moon base!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Slaine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Lemrina...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me apologize for the many wrongs
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I have rendered unto you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Slaine...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray for your well-being.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.79,0:05:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Harklight, escort Her Highness to a shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Slaine! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come with me, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I won't leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Slaine! Slaine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're detecting numerous craft exiting the moon base!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Reinforcements?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.03,0:06:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They're leaving the combat area.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The moon base...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is going down?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we beat them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They're self-destructing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Harklight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:06:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Guard the shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Harklight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Harklight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I ordered you to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Harklight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Stygis Squadron! Don't act on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.95,0:07:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Reinforcements closing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy at ten o'clock, ten degrees down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.25,0:07:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand by to engage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! We no longer have any hope of winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't throw your lives away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I made my peace with death long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow me this one selfish act.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender, Harklight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Sir Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But I cannot comply with that order.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:07:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All units, scatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How could they do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Those moves...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, Harklight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let it end like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still something I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come for you, Slaine Troyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's settle this once and for all, Kaizuka Inaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Reading my moves won't do you any good if you can't get away from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who isn't getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:09:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Opening contact channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Decrypting protocols.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt this will do any good, but I'll ask anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you surrender, Slaine Troyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come all this way just to \Ntell me poor jokes, Kaizuka Inaho?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I have a different objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't disappoint me, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! My monitors are damaged?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. We can't do any more high-load processing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut all predictive imagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I no longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,need a future!{lmao this line}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Incoming at two o'clock, five degrees up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All ahead, emergency speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come about, 060!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming about, 060!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Load canister shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire once targets are locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nao's combat data is stored in the tactical data link.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.67,0:11:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All units, refer to that and—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Barouhcruz of the Orbital Knights' Thirty-Seven Clans reporting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,May I intrude?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Count Barouhcruz...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Incoming at eight o'clock, twenty-five degrees down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Intercept!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Three rounds remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.84,0:12:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing to be gained by continuing to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed. But there is nothing to be lost, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving in to despair is a foolish choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You just don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is precisely what I've wanted all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Slice them to ribbons!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Rayet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Radar returns approaching fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Tharsis... and a Terran Cataphract!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:12:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Rayet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Three-direction crossfire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,MRSI, neutralize target, auto fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always loathed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that wretched color!{dying}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Harklight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The drones are on autopilot! Use the rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We can limit the direction of their attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I only lost an arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Harklight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Battle status?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Three Stygis Masters remain, myself included,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as some six Slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest have been felled by Terran forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am perilously low on ammunition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Count Barouhcruz.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Octantis' right arm is out of commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been damaged in that last attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,These Terran warriors are not without skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I should expect as much from Sir Slaine's birthplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Fight not an Olympus sandstorm," eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We seem to have misread the winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us join in battle once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy formation closing in at \Nnine o'clock, twenty degrees up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All guns, take aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.23,0:14:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Cataphract platoons: all units fire at will!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll act as a drogue chute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It will stabilize your descent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You intend to die with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll burn up on re-entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Cataphract frames are high density.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll work well enough as ablative shielding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible. They'll never last.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so? I guess we'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A shooting star!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.99,0:16:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Special report.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.56,0:16:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Aldnoah Reactor #1, constructed as a sign of goodwill between Earth and Vers,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is scheduled to be activated today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:17:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're told that Empress Asseylum herself \Nwill participate in the activation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Research into unrestricted activation privileges for all is still ongoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When that is achieved, it will signal \Nthe birth of Aldnoah-based industries
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that will help greatly with \Nthe Earth's reconstruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And for the Vers Empire, \Nprovider of Aldnoah technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,it should prove an effective means \Nto earn foreign capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Troyard's theories have already been proven,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so we should see them put into practice \Nin the near future.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.87,0:17:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ironic that Slaine Troyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the son of that same Dr. Troyard, was the one who plotted the assassination of Empress Asseylum
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and served as the trigger for Interplanetary War II.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Slaine Troyard's death allowed Earth and Vers \Nto settle upon a friendship treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there are still Mars Knights who continue to occupy territory on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.06,0:17:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,One goal of Empress Asseylum's visit \Nis peace negotiations with those knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:18:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's hoping that we'll see the prompt return \Nof that occupied territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,May this light
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,form a bridge of peace between Earth and Vers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.97,0:18:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You really should eat your meals, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.19,0:18:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had complaints from the warden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Your move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that from when I shot you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I replaced it with an analytical engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A biomechanical implant that was neuro-linked to my cranial nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But I had it removed. I don't need it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hasn't this gone long enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I deceived. I stole. I killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I sacrificed countless numbers of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You're going to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.54,0:19:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you save me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one more request.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Princess Asseylum's.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, save Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.00,0:19:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Save Slaine Troyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Save him from the cycle of misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.32,0:19:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Seylum asked me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:19:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.67,0:20:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.31,0:20:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The blue sky and ocean go on as far as the eye can see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.57,0:20:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm told that the blue sky is the result \Nof something called Rayleigh scattering.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite well-informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When I visited Earth last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.71,0:20:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,a Terran I had befriended \Nwas kind enough to teach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a cherished memory of mine.
